template<class Key, class HashFcn = __gnu_cxx::hash<Key>>
void PriorityQueue< Key, HashFcn >::insert ( const Key &  k,
double  priority,
bool  add = false 
) [inline]

Adds an element to the queue with the given priority.

Parameters:
k The key to insert
priority The priority to give to k
add Determines the behavior if k already exists. If true, then priority is added to the existing priority. If false, the new priority is used if it exceeds the existing priority.
